BH/BlastRage


BH stops polishing his gun and looks to BlastRage. "So they are 
attacking the Predacon, I hear." Bh then sends a com to Koga Shuko. 
"Koga, I hear that all of you newcomer's are attacking the
Predacon's, 
Do you want us to help?" 

Blastrage looks at the ground. "Ants, I just hate ants!" Blastrage 
starts burning the ant pile. "Hehehe take that, you stupid ants!" 
Blastrage starts jumping on the ant pile putting out the fire that
was 
starting. Blastrage then hears BH's comment. "Don't the Predacin's 
have an ant named Inferno. I will kill him, hehehe."
